    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Albert V. Roe, l. w. w. leader,\ncharged with conspiracy, was found\nguilty of the offense this morning\nby Justice George w. Stocker and\nsentenced to spend three months\nin the county Jail.\n\n\nSaturday afternoon Roe demand\ned~a jury trial. but this morning he\nhad changed his mind and even re-\nfused to testify in his own behalf."
